{"content": "<p>The MintFace website is 1 year young this week and to celebrate we have refreshed our site building in three brand new areas from the artist features over the last year. </p><h3 id=\"new-categories\">New Categories</h3><p>You asked for better sorting of different art by category so we listened. You can now view art by <a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/tag/1-1s/\">1/1s</a>, <a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/tag/photography/\">photography</a>, <a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/tag/generative/\">generative art</a> or <a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/page/2\">latest news</a> easily.  </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-11.59.02-AM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1998\" height=\"1388\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-11.59.02-AM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-11.59.02-AM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-11.59.02-AM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-11.59.02-AM.png 1998w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>MintFace <a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/\">photography category</a></figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"new-nft-skills-youtube-channel\">New NFT Skills YouTube Channel</h3><p>There is a new <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCgi6FuK44ld1v0ld4bKj7ww\">NFT Skills YouTube channel</a> featuring videos to help your frens get confident with NFTs. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-12.01.18-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1267\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-12.01.18-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-12.01.18-PM.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-12.01.18-PM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-12.01.18-PM.png 2326w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><h3 id=\"mintface-support-membership\">MintFace Support Membership</h3><p>Having so many supporters of the MintFace platform makes it possible to keep featuring artists and provide opportunities to be seen. </p><p>It is completely optional to become a membership because you <em>literally get nothing different!</em> </p><p>Instead, your support is an acknowledgment that you get value what we do, and would like us to keep going.</p><p>You can <a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup/6104dbc7f2650b002f6f962c/yearly\">become a MintFace supporter</a> today or drop 0.05 eth to mintface.eth and your membership will be upgraded. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup/6104dbc7f2650b002f6f962c/yearly\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-12.23.05-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1564\" height=\"708\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-12.23.05-PM.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-12.23.05-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2022/05/Screen-Shot-2022-05-24-at-12.23.05-PM.png 1564w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/#/portal/signup/6104dbc7f2650b002f6f962c/yearly\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Become A MintFace Supporter</a></div><hr /><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/11/tenor.gif\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"498\" height=\"300\"></figure>"}